Package org.zurdavid.petrinets.controller

Class BoundednessAnalysisResult

java.lang.Object
org.zurdavid.petrinets.controller.BoundednessAnalysisResult
public class BoundednessAnalysisResult extends Object
The class is a data class. It contains the data resulting from a boundedness analysis.
